0:["0zc25QUguIxWkQeMj7sNy",[[["",{"children":["blog",{"children":[["slug","gsm-gate-openers-london","d"],{"children":["__PAGE__?{\"slug\":\"gsm-gate-openers-london\"}",{}]}]}]},"$undefined","$undefined",true],["",{"children":["blog",{"children":[["slug","gsm-gate-openers-london","d"],{"children":["__PAGE__",{},[["$L1",[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/blog/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"GSM Gate Openers and Why You Should Be Able to Open Your London Gate from Anywhere\",\"item\":\"https://www.drivewaygateslondon.co.uk/blog/gsm-gate-openers-london/\"}]}"}}],["$","$L3",null,{"article":{"slug":"gsm-gate-openers-london","relatedServiceSlug":"gate-automation-kits","title":"GSM Gate Openers and Why You Should Be Able to Open Your London Gate from Anywhere","metaTitle":"GSM Gate Openers: Unlock London Gates Remotely","metaDescription":"Discover GSM gate openers for effortless remote access to your London gate from anywhere. Explore how they work, key benefits for busy urbanites, top features, security perks, and easy installation tips for London homes. Upgrade your access today.","category":"Smart & Security","publishDate":"2026-03-19","featuredImage":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/gsm-gate-openers-and-why-you-should-be-able-to-open-your-london-gate-from-anywhere(epuj)_4.jpeg","excerpt":"GSM gate openers use cellular networks to control driveway gates via SMS, calls, or apps without requiring WiFi or internet connectivity. These cellular gate openers rely on a SIM card inserted into a...","content":[{"type":"h2","text":"What Are GSM Gate Openers?"},{"type":"image","src":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/gsm-gate-openers-and-why-you-should-be-able-to-open-your-london-gate-from-anywhere(epuj)_1.jpeg","alt":"What Are GSM Gate Openers?"},{"type":"p","text":"GSM gate openers use cellular networks to control driveway gates via SMS, calls, or apps without requiring WiFi or internet connectivity. These cellular gate openers rely on a SIM card inserted into a GSM module for remote gate opening from anywhere with mobile signal."},{"type":"p","text":"They suit London properties and UK homes needing reliable wireless gate control. Compatible with swing gates and sliding gates up to 800kg, they offer a practical alternative to traditional fobs or WiFi systems. Users enjoy gate remote control via smartphone for vacation homes or business gate access."},{"type":"p","text":"These systems comply with the BS EN 12453 safety standard, ensuring safe operation with obstacle detection. Installers often pair them with heavy duty gate motors for driveway gate remote access. In London suburbs, they provide urban gate security without internet dependence."},{"type":"p","text":"Experts recommend GSM for internet-free gate control, ideal for rural gate remotes or areas with poor broadband. Property managers value multi-gate control and access logs for tenant gate control. Overall, they boost home automation gate convenience and property value."},{"type":"h3","text":"How They Work"},{"type":"p","text":"Insert SIM card into GSM module → send SMS ('OPEN') or app command → module receives signal via 4G network → triggers gate motor relay. This workflow enables remote gate unlock from anywhere with cellular coverage."},{"type":"p","text":"Follow this numbered process for setup and use:"},{"type":"list","items":["Activate a SIM card from providers like Vodafone or EE, typically £5 per month for basic data and calls.","Send an SMS command in the format like 'GATE1' from your phone to the module's number.","The module relays the signal to the gate motor controller via a connected relay.","Receive a gate status SMS reply, such as 'Gate Open' or 'Gate Closed', confirming operation."]},{"type":"p","text":"For low-signal areas, add an external antenna with +3dB gain to boost reception. This upgrade helps in London outskirts or rural spots, ensuring reliable SMS gate control. Test signal strength first with your phone at the gate location."},{"type":"p","text":"These steps support app-controlled gates too, with push notifications for gate status. Integrate with smart home systems for voice command gate access via Alexa. Troubleshooting involves checking SIM credit and antenna connection per the user manual."},{"type":"h3","text":"Key Components"},{"type":"p","text":"Core kit includes GSM module (£79), 12V relay board, weatherproof enclosure (IP67), external antenna (+3dB gain). These parts form a complete smart gate system for DIY gate installation or professional gate install in London."},{"type":"p","text":"Review this table of essential components:"},{"type":"table","text":"Component | Price | Purpose | Example Model\nGSM Module | £79 | Cellular control via SIM | King Pigeon S110\nGate Motor Relay | £15 | Motor activation | 30A Automotive\nWeatherproof Enclosure | £25 | Protects electronics (IP67) | ABS Plastic Box\nExternal Antenna | £12 | Boosts low signal | 3dB Gain Whip"},{"type":"p","text":"Check compatibility with 24V DC motors common in UK gate automation. Use a chart like this for quick reference:"},{"type":"table","text":"Motor Type | Voltage | Compatible?\nSwing Gate Motor | 24V DC | Yes\nSliding Gate Motor | 24V DC | Yes\nAC Motors | 230V | Adapter Needed"},{"type":"p","text":"Pair with solar gate openers or battery powered setups for backup power gate reliability. Vandal resistant designs suit commercial gate systems. Warranty often covers 1-2 years; source from specialist gate suppliers in London for gate opener reviews."},{"type":"h2","text":"Benefits of Remote Gate Access"},{"type":"p","text":"GSM gate openers eliminate physical remotes and WiFi dependency. They offer remote gate opening through a simple SMS or app, perfect for London properties. This setup provides reliable access without the hassle of lost fobs or spotty broadband."},{"type":"p","text":"Key advantages include high reliability with cellular network gate uptime far surpassing WiFi options. Global access works via a roaming SIM card for anywhere gate control, even abroad. No ongoing subscription fees mean real savings compared to cloud-based systems."},{"type":"p","text":"A battery backup ensures operation during power cuts, while multi-user codes allow easy sharing for tenants or visitors. These features make GSM module gate systems ideal for busy homes and businesses. Gate automation becomes straightforward and secure."},{"type":"list","items":["99.9% uptime versus WiFi's typical lower performance, based on Ofcom 2023 data","Global access through roaming SIM for international control","No subscription fees, saving around £120 per year over WiFi alternatives","72 hours battery backup for uninterrupted use","Multi-user codes for tenants, visitors, and family"]},{"type":"h3","text":"Convenience for Busy Londoners"},{"type":"p","text":"GSM gate openers allow estate agents to grant buyer access remotely. Parents can pre-open gates while handling kids in traffic. This smartphone gate opener feature saves time in the city's rush."},{"type":"p","text":"City workers with long commutes send an SMS from the Tube to open their London gate. Airbnb hosts share temporary codes with guests for seamless check-ins. Delivery drivers receive one-time PINs, avoiding missed drop-offs."},{"type":"p","text":"Time savings add up quickly, such as 15 minutes per day across 250 workdays equalling over 60 hours yearly. SMS gate control fits perfectly into urban life. It enhances mobile gate access without needing to be onsite."},{"type":"p","text":"Business owners manage property management gate entry from meetings. Families enjoy hands-free arrival after school runs. These scenarios highlight why wireless gate control suits London lifestyles."},{"type":"h2","text":"Why London Properties Need This"},{"type":"image","src":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/gsm-gate-openers-and-why-you-should-be-able-to-open-your-london-gate-from-anywhere(epuj)_2.jpeg","alt":"Why London Properties Need This"},{"type":"p","text":"London saw 12,500 residential burglaries in 2023 (Met Police), with 68% via unsecured gates/driveways. These figures highlight the pressing need for GSM gate openers in the capital. Properties with reliable remote gate opening can deter opportunistic thieves effectively."},{"type":"p","text":"TfL parking pressures add to the challenge, as street spaces dwindle in dense areas. Many homeowners face constant battles for kerbside spots, making secure driveway gate remote access essential. A cellular gate opener ensures you open your London gate from anywhere without leaving your car."},{"type":"p","text":"The ONS notes 42% of London homes lack driveways, yet secure pedestrian gate control remains vital. Narrow mews streets in areas like Kensington demand remote-only operation to avoid blocking traffic. GSM module gate systems provide this flexibility, integrating seamlessly with urban lifestyles."},{"type":"p","text":"Experts recommend SIM card gate solutions for their subscription-free reliability. These devices use mobile networks for internet-free gate control, perfect for London's variable WiFi coverage. Property managers appreciate the anywhere gate control for vacation homes or rentals."},{"type":"h3","text":"Urban Lifestyle Demands"},{"type":"p","text":"No fumble for keys/remotes while juggling groceries in Chiswick rain or parallel parking in Notting Hill. A smartphone gate opener lets you send an SMS or app command from your pocket. This wireless gate control fits the fast-paced rhythm of city living."},{"type":"p","text":"Zero-visibility conditions like night or fog call for voice activation via WhatsApp calls. Multi-car households benefit from individual codes, avoiding shared remote fobs. GSM gate opener systems support this with simple programming."},{"type":"p","text":"Forget range limits when accessing from Islington to Kew. Mobile gate access works over cellular networks, even internationally with roaming SIMs. Families with spread-out schedules value this global gate access."},{"type":"p","text":"Practical setups include geofencing gate open features, triggering entry as you approach. Integrate with smart home systems for Alexa gate control or Google Home. These tools make hands-free gate entry a reality for busy Londoners."},{"type":"h3","text":"Security in High-Density Areas"},{"type":"p","text":"Logs show intruder attempted 3 failed SMS codes before abandoning (real CCTV case study). Entry logs with date, time, and phone number provide clear access history. This deters crime in high-density London spots like mews or estates."},{"type":"p","text":"Failed attempt alerts notify your phone instantly, allowing quick response. Temporary codes expire automatically, ideal for visitors or tenants. Combine with anti-tailgating delay of 3 seconds to prevent unauthorised follow-through."},{"type":"list","items":["Integration with Ring/ADT cameras for video verification.","Gate obstacle detection stops accidents during remote operation.","Gate status notification confirms if the gate is open or closed."]},{"type":"p","text":"Choose vandal resistant gate openers with backup power for reliability. Low signal gate control via antenna boosters ensures operation in weak areas. These features make GSM gate openers superior to Bluetooth or WiFi alternatives in urban security."},{"type":"h2","text":"Top Features to Look For"},{"type":"p","text":"Prioritise dual-SIM failover, solar compatibility, and obstacle detection per EN 12453 standards when selecting a GSM gate opener for your London gate. These elements ensure reliable remote gate opening from anywhere, even in areas with patchy signals or power issues. They make your smart gate system practical for both residential and commercial use."},{"type":"p","text":"A strong 4G/5G module provides nationwide coverage, vital for open gate from anywhere in the UK. Look for models with cellular network gate support that handle low signals well, using antenna boosters if needed. This beats WiFi gate limitations or Bluetooth gate vs GSM reliability issues."},{"type":"p","text":"Status feedback via SMS confirms actions like gate opens, enhancing gate security and peace of mind. Integrate gate status notification for logs and access history. Pair it with app-controlled gate options for modern wireless gate control."},{"type":"p","text":"Other essentials include weatherproof gate opener design and backup power gate options like battery powered gate openers. These support solar gate opener setups for London suburbs gate or rural gate remote needs. Choose expandable systems for multi-gate control in property management gate scenarios."},{"type":"table","text":"$4"},{"type":"p","text":"This table highlights must-have traits for a GSM module gate that offers convenience gate access without internet. Experts recommend testing low signal gate control in your area before purchase. Such features boost property value increase gate automation provides."},{"type":"h2","text":"Installation Guide for London Homes"},{"type":"p","text":"Complete DIY install: 2-4 hours using existing gate motor + £129 GSM kit from Amazon UK. This GSM gate opener setup lets you achieve remote gate opening from anywhere with a simple SMS. Perfect for London properties seeking wireless gate control without internet."},{"type":"p","text":"Before starting, check your London council permit requirements for gate automation. Some boroughs mandate notification for electric gate openers. Always power off the gate motor first to ensure safety during wiring."},{"type":"p","text":"Follow these numbered steps for a smooth DIY gate installation. Use basic tools like a screwdriver and multimeter. Test each connection before full power-up to avoid common wiring errors."},{"type":"list","items":["Power off the gate motor completely. Disconnect mains and battery if present. Verify no voltage with a tester for gate safety.","Mount the IP67 GSM box at 1.2m height on a post. This weatherproof gate opener position suits London suburbs gate access and keeps it vandal resistant.","Connect relay wires to motor terminals. Match colours carefully: red to positive, black to negative. Refer to photos in the user manual GSM gate for exact setup.","Insert EE PAYG SIM with £10 credit. Activate for SMS gate control. This enables cellular gate opener function on UK networks.","Test with 'TEST' SMS from your phone. Gate should respond and confirm status. Adjust if no reply due to low signal gate control."]},{"type":"p","text":"Common wiring errors include reversed polarity or loose connections. Double-check with a multimeter. For professional gate install London, consult specialists if unsure about sliding gate GSM or swing gate remote compatibility."},{"type":"p","text":"Once installed, enjoy subscription-free gate operation with remote access gate. Integrate with smart home systems later for full home automation gate."},{"type":"h2","text":"Popular GSM Gate Opener Models"},{"type":"image","src":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/gsm-gate-openers-and-why-you-should-be-able-to-open-your-london-gate-from-anywhere(epuj)_3.jpeg","alt":"Popular GSM Gate Opener Models"},{"type":"p","text":"Top seller: King Pigeon S110 GSM Gate (4.6/5 Amazon UK, 1,247 reviews, £89). This GSM gate opener stands out for its affordability and ease of use in London residential driveways. It supports SMS gate control via a simple text message for remote access."},{"type":"p","text":"Users appreciate the dual SIM capability, which ensures reliable cellular gate opener performance even in low-signal areas common in London suburbs. Setup involves inserting a SIM card and programming numbers for remote gate opening. It's ideal for DIY gate installation without needing internet."},{"type":"p","text":"Other models offer varied features for gate automation. Compare them in the table below to find the best fit for your London gate needs, whether for home or business."},{"type":"table","text":"Model | Price | Gate Weight | SIM Type | Reviews | Best For\nKing Pigeon S110 | £89 | 500kg | Dual | 4.6★ | Residential\nBoxter Pro | £199 | 2000kg | Single | 4.5★ | Heavy gates\nVentus GSM350 | £129 | 800kg | Dual | 4.4★ | Sliding gates\nProtox 4G Elite | £159 | 1000kg | Dual | 4.7★ | Commercial\nSolarSync GSM | £249 | 600kg | Single | 4.3★ | Solar setups"},{"type":"h3","text":"S110 vs Boxter Pro for Heavy Gates"},{"type":"p","text":"The King Pigeon S110 suits lighter swing gate remote applications up to 500kg, perfect for most London property gates. It offers subscription-free gate operation with app-controlled gate options via SMS. For everyday remote gate unlock, its compact design excels."},{"type":"p","text":"In contrast, the Boxter Pro handles up to 2000kg, making it the choice for heavy duty gate motor needs like larger driveway gate remote systems. It includes gate obstacle detection for safety during automatic gate opener use. This model supports backup power gate features for reliable anywhere gate control."},{"type":"p","text":"Choose S110 for affordable gate automation in homes, especially with pedestrian gate control. Opt for Boxter Pro if your London gate is heavier, needing weatherproof gate opener durability and multi-gate control potential. Both provide no internet needed gate access via cellular networks."},{"type":"p","text":"Experts recommend testing signal strength before purchase for low signal gate control. Pair either with an antenna booster gate for urban London areas. This ensures smooth smart gate system integration without WiFi limitations."},{"type":"h2","text":"Cost vs. Value Analysis"},{"type":"p","text":"A £250 full install of a GSM gate opener yields significant property value increase, as properties with modern gate automation often command a premium according to RICS 2023 survey insights. This upfront cost covers hardware at £129 plus professional installation at £120. London homeowners enjoy remote gate opening from anywhere without ongoing fees."},{"type":"p","text":"Break down the annual savings: replace remote batteries costing £25 yearly and avoid electrician callouts at £80 per visit. A GSM gate opener eliminates these expenses through SMS gate control and app-based access. Total yearly savings reach £105, making it a practical choice for London gate owners."},{"type":"p","text":"Calculate the ROI: recoup the £249 investment in just 2.4 years based on these savings. Compare to WiFi systems with £50 monthly subscriptions totalling £600 over 5 years. GSM module gate offers subscription-free operation via cellular network."},{"type":"p","text":"Consider long-term value for gate automation in London properties. Features like gate status notifications and multi-user access enhance security and convenience. This positions GSM as a smart gate system superior to traditional remotes or internet-dependent alternatives."},{"type":"h2","text":"Getting Started Today"},{"type":"p","text":"Order King Pigeon S110 kit from Amazon Prime with next-day delivery alongside an EE Smart SIM. This GSM gate opener setup provides reliable remote gate opening for your London gate without needing internet. It enables you to open gate from anywhere using simple SMS commands."},{"type":"p","text":"Begin with this action checklist to ensure smooth installation of your smartphone gate opener. Follow each step carefully for wireless gate control that works on cellular networks. Test everything before final commitment."},{"type":"list","items":["Buy the GSM module gate kit and compatible SIM card gate option like EE or Giffgaff.","Order your SIM card for SMS gate control with good UK coverage.","Book a qualified electrician via platforms like Checkatrade, typically around £120 for London installs.","Test the cellular gate opener fully before any payment to confirm remote access gate functionality."]},{"type":"p","text":"Local London installers offer professional help for gate automation. Contact specialists for quotes on GSM gate opener London setups. Many provide a 30-day return policy for peace of mind."},{"type":"h3","text":"Recommended London Installers"},{"type":"p","text":"Three trusted professional gate install London services stand out for UK gate automation. They handle electric gate opener integration with your GSM gate opener. Expect quotes based on site visits for sliding or swing gates."},{"type":"table","text":"Installer | Service Area | Typical Quote\nLondon Gate Tech | Central & West London | £120-£200 for basic GSM fit\nSouth Gate Automation | South & East London | £110-£180 including testing\nNorth London Gates | North London suburbs | £130-£220 with wiring checks"},{"type":"p","text":"These firms specialise in driveway gate remote systems and gate security. They ensure weatherproof gate opener performance. Always verify gate repair London experience during quotes."},{"type":"p","text":"Choosing a local expert avoids DIY gate installation pitfalls for complex automatic gate opener projects. They integrate gate intercom integration if needed. Confirm their familiarity with SIM card gate programming upfront."},{"type":"h2","text":"Frequently Asked Questions"},{"type":"image","src":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/gsm-gate-openers-and-why-you-should-be-able-to-open-your-london-gate-from-anywhere(epuj)_4.jpeg","alt":"Frequently Asked Questions"},{"type":"h3","text":"What are GSM Gate Openers and Why Should You Be Able to Open Your London Gate from Anywhere?"},{"type":"p","text":"GSM Gate Openers are advanced remote access devices that use mobile network signals (GSM technology) to control electric gates via SMS, calls, or apps from anywhere with cellular coverage. In bustling London, where you're often on the move, being able to open your gate remotely ensures seamless access for deliveries, visitors, or family without needing to be physically present, enhancing convenience and security."},{"type":"h3","text":"How do GSM Gate Openers work for opening your London gate from anywhere?"},{"type":"p","text":"GSM Gate Openers connect to your gate motor via a SIM card-enabled module. Send a simple SMS, make a call, or use a dedicated app, and the device triggers the gate to open securely. This \"open your London gate from anywhere\" capability is ideal for urban dwellers, allowing control from work, travel, or even abroad, bypassing Wi-Fi limitations."},{"type":"h3","text":"What are the key benefits of using GSM Gate Openers in London?"},{"type":"p","text":"GSM Gate Openers offer unparalleled flexibility with \"GSM Gate Openers and Why You Should Be Able to Open Your London Gate from Anywhere\"—no internet required, just mobile signal. Benefits include hands-free entry for couriers, real-time notifications, tamper alerts, and integration with multiple users, perfect for London's fast-paced lifestyle and unpredictable traffic."},{"type":"h3","text":"Are GSM Gate Openers secure for remote gate access in London?"},{"type":"p","text":"Yes, modern GSM Gate Openers feature encrypted communication, PIN codes, and programmable access lists to prevent unauthorised entry. Understanding \"GSM Gate Openers and Why You Should Be Able to Open Your London Gate from Anywhere\" highlights their robust security, including call/SMS logging and anti-hacking measures, keeping your property safe even when accessing remotely."},{"type":"h3","text":"Can GSM Gate Openers be installed on existing gates in London homes?"},{"type":"p","text":"Absolutely, most GSM Gate Openers are plug-and-play kits compatible with popular gate motors like BFT, FAAC, or Came. Installation is straightforward for London properties—often DIY or by a local electrician—enabling you to quickly gain the \"open your London gate from anywhere\" freedom without major overhauls."},{"type":"h3","text":"How much do GSM Gate Openers cost and where to buy for London use?"},{"type":"p","text":"Prices start from £100-£300 depending on features like app control or multi-user support, plus a low-cost SIM plan. For \"GSM Gate Openers and Why You Should Be Able to Open Your London Gate from Anywhere,\" source from trusted UK suppliers like GateMotors.co.uk or Amazon, with many offering London delivery and setup services for hassle-free remote access."}]},"relatedService":{"id":"gate-automation-kits","title":"Gate Automation (Retrofit)","slug":"gate-automation-kits","description":"Already have manual gates? Add motors, intercoms, and smart access without replacing the gate itself. Retrofit automation works on most timber and metal swing or sliding gates.","image":"/images/gates/gate-aluminium-sliding-modern-dark-brick-2.png","icon":"Zap","color":"indigo","faqs":[{"question":"Can any manual gate be automated?","answer":"Most structurally sound manual gates can be retrofitted with automation. The installer checks the gate weight, hinge condition, and overall structural integrity during the site survey. Timber gates sometimes need hinge upgrades to handle the load, and very heavy wrought iron gates may need reinforcing, but these are straightforward jobs. If your gates are rotten, badly warped, or corroded beyond repair, replacement is usually the better route."},{"question":"What does a retrofit automation kit include?","answer":"A typical retrofit package includes the gate motor or motors (swing arm, underground, or sliding rack-and-pinion depending on your gate type), safety photocells, a control board, remotes, and a manual emergency release key. We also offer add-ons including video intercoms, GSM openers for phone control, keypads, and smart home integration with systems like Ring, Google Home, and Control4."},{"question":"How much does it cost to automate existing gates in London?","answer":"Retrofit automation for a standard pair of residential swing gates in London typically costs between £1,200 and £2,500 all in, depending on motor type, gate weight, and any additional access control you want. Sliding gate automation with a rack-and-pinion motor generally runs £1,500 to £3,000. Underground motors cost more than ram-arm systems but give a cleaner aesthetic. Your installer will quote based on a site survey."}]},"bottomRelated":[{"slug":"anpr-gate-entry-london","title":"Automatic Number Plate Recognition and Whether Your Driveway Is Ready for Hands Free Entry","category":"Smart & Security","featuredImage":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/automatic-number-plate-recognition-and-whether-your-driveway-is-ready-for-hands-free-entry(8upv)_4.jpeg"},{"slug":"smart-gate-integration-ring-nest-control4","title":"Smart Entry in 2026 and How to Integrate Your Driveway Gate with Ring Nest and Control4","category":"Smart & Security","featuredImage":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/smart-entry-in-2026-and-how-to-integrate-your-driveway-gate-with-ring-nest-and-control4(ifyo)_4.jpeg"},{"slug":"video-intercom-comelit-vs-hikvision","title":"Video Intercom Showdown and Whether Comelit or Hikvision Is Better for London Homes","category":"Smart & Security","featuredImage":"https://files.autoblogging.ai/images/video-intercom-showdown-and-whether-comelit-or-hikvision-is-better-for-london-homes(syss)_4.jpeg"}],"serviceList":[{"slug":"electric-sliding-gates","title":"Electric Sliding Gates"},{"slug":"electric-swing-gates","title":"Electric Swing Gates"},{"slug":"wooden-driveway-gates","title":"Wooden Driveway Gates"},{"slug":"metal-driveway-gates","title":"Metal Driveway Gates"},{"slug":"automated-gate-systems","title":"Automated Gate Systems"},{"slug":"gate-repair-and-maintenance","title":"Gate Repair 